<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>107</hymn_number>
<title>NOT ALL THE BLOOD</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Juda maicham chunga,
 Gan thah cheng thisan in;
 Lunggil gilo a muonsak puoi,
 Gitloh a sawp thieng puoi.

[V2]
 2. Van Belam No Krista'n,
 Gitloh cheng A lamang;
 Kithawihna lopi zaw ahi,
 Gan thi sanga lul zaw.

[V3]
 3. Puokgik Na puok mudi'n,
 Na luchang deihum chuh;
 Lunggil kisik in ka dinga,
 Gitloh thupha chawiin.

[V4]
 4. Puokgik Na puok mudi'n,
 Ka thagau in a en;
 Hansie dawl thinga Na kikhaih,
 Gitloh na puok a he'i.</lyrics>
</song>